      • burn

        public Flame burn(Flame evs)
        Method manages the burn process on a flame instance. Each null pair gets burned with probability exc. The flame changes get tested one by one by calculating target and selecting the best choice with a probability depending on the difference between target values
        Parameters:
        evs - : Flame instance to operate on
        Returns:
        Flame : burned Flame instance
